pped%200.8%25%20to%20%C2%A38.91%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20valuing%20the%20bank%20at%20about%20%C2%A3160%20billion%20(%24201%20billion.)%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlans%20to%20trim%20personnel%20expense%20by%208%25%20over%202025%20and%202026%20are%20positive%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20eye-catching%20overhaul%20or%20cost%20cutting%20measures%20in%20the%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Makdad%2C%20senior%20equity%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20increasing%20efficiency%20at%20a%20bank%20like%20HSBC%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20many%20small%20and%20midsize%20details%20that%20have%20to%20be%20well%20coordinated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHSBC%20reported%20annual%20pre-tax%20profits%20of%20%2432.3%20billion%2C%20up%20%242%20billion%20on%202023%20but%20short%20of%20estimates%20by%20LSEG%20analysts%20of%20%2432.63%20billion.%20Revenues%20were%20%2465.85%20billion%2C%20surpassing%20forecasts%20of%20%2466.52%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20are%20the%20first%20under%20former%20CFO%20Georges%20Elhedery%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20CEO%20in%20September%20from%20Noel%20Quinn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElhedery's%20cost-cutting%20plans%20include%20simplifying%20HSBC's%20structure.%20Its%20Asia-Pacific%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%20will%20form%20the%20%26quot%3Beastern%20markets%26quot%3B%20division%2C%20while%20its%20UK%2C%20European%2C%20and%20Americas%20business%20will%20be%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bwestern%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20unveiled%20a%20new%20international%20wealth%20and%20premier%20banking%20unit%20and%20will%20reduce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhsbc-middle-managers-reapply-jobs-layoffs-big-four-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20investment%20banker%20headcount%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20creating%20a%20simple%2C%20more%20agile%2C%20focused%20bank%20built%20on%20our%20core%20strengths%2C%26quot%3B%20Elhedery%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20take%20deliberate%20and%20decisive%20steps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHSBC%20said%20it%20would%20launch%20a%20share%20buyback%20worth%20up%20to%20%242%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Hunter%20at%20Interactive%20Investors%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BChanging%20horses%20midstream%20is%20never%20an%20easy%20task%2C%20and%20the%20previously%20announced%20transformation%20will%20have%20upfront%20costs%20which%20will%20delay%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20anticipated%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20rationale%20for%20a%20more%20focused%20operation%20is%20clear%20and%20should%20allow%20the%20group%20to%20reap%20the%20rewards%20of%20a%20higher%20focus%20on%20profit%20generation%2C%20while%20also%20keeping%20costs%20in%20check.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20analysts%20said%20in%20a%20note%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20restructuring%20headlines%20in%20line%20with%20pre-results%3C%2Fspan%3E%20press%20%3Cspan%3Ewe%20think%20the%20key%20question%20for%20investors%20given%20the%20strength%20in%20the%20share%20year-to-date%20and%20relative%20complexity%20of%20the%20group%20is%20whether%20HSBC%E2%80%89offers%20premium%20long-term%20growth%20at%20an%20attractive%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhsbc-cost-cuts-share-buyback-georges-elhedery-layoffs-earnings-report-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739970284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5bf807bb3f854015d3623%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhsbc-cost-cuts-share-buyback-georges-elhedery-layoffs-earnings-report-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20London-headquartered%20bank%20plans%20to%20save%20%24300%20million%20this%20year%20and%20aims%20to%20reduc