epeat%20rape%20offenders%20to%20walk%20free.%20The%20accused%2C%20Ramesh%20Singh%2C%20has%20a%20horrifying%20history%20of%20crimes%20against%20minors%20but%20was%20repeatedly%20acquitted%20by%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Trail%20of%20Crimes%2C%20a%20Broken%20System%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20Singh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Dabripura%20in%20Polaykala%2C%20raped%20a%205-year-old%20girl%20in%20Shajapur%20district's%20Mubarikpur%20village%20back%20in%202003.%20He%20was%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20in%20prison.%20But%20after%20serving%20his%20sentence%20and%20being%20released%20in%202013%2C%20he%20struck%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20he%20kidnapped%20and%20brutally%20raped%20an%208-year-old%20girl%20in%20Ashta%20(Sehore).%20This%20time%2C%20the%20lower%20court%20sentenced%20him%20to%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20overturned%20the%20verdict%20on%20technical%20grounds%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20victim's%20father%20was%20present%20during%20the%20identification%20parade%2C%20which%20could%20have%20influenced%20the%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20gave%20Ramesh%20another%20chance%20to%20walk%20free.%20Another%20innocent%20child%20paid%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20February%202025%20Horror%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20February%201-2%2C%20an%2011-year-old%20deaf%20and%20mute%20girl%20went%20missing%20from%20her%20home%20in%20Narsinghgarh.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20she%20was%20found%20in%20the%20bushes%2C%20her%20body%20bearing%20brutal%20injuries.%20A%20medical%20examination%20confirmed%20the%20assault.%20As%20her%20condition%20worsened%2C%20she%20was%20rushed%20to%20Hamidia%20Hospital%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20where%20she%20died%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20acting%20as%20the%20complainant%2C%20launched%20an%20intense%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%2