2%80%94%20or%20her%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20is%20now%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-fore-street-portland-maine-review-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJames%20Beard-nominated%3C%2Fa%3E%20owner%20and%20chef%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.besharamrestaurant.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBesharam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20regional%20Gujarati%20restaurant%20in%20San%20Francisco%20that%20pays%20tribute%20to%20the%20dishes%20of%20her%20heritage%20and%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20my%20guests%20step%20outside%20their%20comfort%20zones%2C%20I%20do%20the%20same%20with%20them%2C%20trusting%20they'll%20embrace%20my%20menu%20with%20an%20open%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20I%20hope%20to%20put%20Gujarati%20food%20on%20the%20map.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20also%20hopes%20to%20help%20diners%20expand%20their%20perception%20of%20Indian%20cuisine.%20Here%20are%20her%20tips%20for%20finding%20a%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-how-to-spot-good-high-end-indian-restaurant-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274013c3c-7af0-41ff-ad62-2ea6c125fb02%5C%22%3ELook%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20regional%20dishes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Heena%20Patel%20of%20Besharam%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae689b6630eb10385c9b4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeena%20Patel%20is%20the%20owner%20and%20chef%20of%20Besharam%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Felker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20so%20much%20to%20offer%2C%20and%20each%20dish%20is%20rich%20with%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20said.%20%26quot%3BGrow