0Uttar%20Pradesh%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20the%20state's%20educational%20issues%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20closure%20of%2011%20lakh%20primary%20schools%2C%20most%20in%20UP.%20SP%20leader%20Mata%20Prasad%20Pandey%20accuses%20Adityanath%20of%20politicizing%20language%20by%20shifting%20the%20focus%20to%20Urdu%2C%20while%20ignoring%20vital%20educational%20improvements.%20Yogi%20counters%20SP's%20stance%20on%20language%20with%20accusations%20of%20double%20standards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fup-cm-careless-towards-education-akhilesh-on-yogis-remark-on-urdu%2Farticleshow%2F118384059.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Mo%2C%20Diversity%2C%20And%20The%20Indian%20Immigrant%20In%20The%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20alien%20were%20to%20gain%20insights%20into%20the%20immigrant%20%E2%80%98situation'%20currently%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Netflix%20show%20%3Cem%3EMo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewould%20act%20as%20a%20good%20gateway.%20Except%2C%20it%20might%20lead%20the%20alien%20to%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20no%20Indian%20immigrants%2C%20legal%20or%20illegal%2C%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20semi-autobiographical%20comedy%20created%20by%20Palestinian-American%20comic%20Mo%20Amer%2C%20along%20with%20Egyptian-American%20Ramy%20Youssef%2C%20traces%20the%20life%20of%20Mohammad%20%E2%80%98Mo'%20Najjar%2C%20whose%20family%20arrived%20in%20Houston%20two%20decades%20ago%20as%20Palestinian%20asylum%20seekers%20from%20Kuwait.%20Through%20two%20seasons%2C%20the%20series%20has%20captured%20the%20hopes%2C%20dreams%2C%20despair%2C%20deceit%2C%20dehumanisation%2C%20discriminatory%20cultural%20practices%2C%20etc.%2C%20that%20define%20the%20immigrant%20experience.%20Mo's%20family%20is%20the%20vehicle%20through%20which%20the%20heated%20ongoing%20debate%20on%20immigration%20in%20the%20US%20is%20carried%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20in%20an%20airy%2C%20easy%20manner.%20Quite%20in%20contrast%20with%20military%20aircrafts%20full%20of%20deported%20illegal%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Are%20The%20Indians%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMo%20grew%20up%20in%20Houston%2C%20speaking%20Arabic%2C%20Spanish%2C%20and%20English%2C%20and%20has%20hustled%20all%20his%20life%20to%20take%20care%20of%20his%20family%20after%20his%20father's%20death.%20His%20struggles%20are%20everyone's%20struggles%2C%20only%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20undocumented%20status%20of%20his%20family.%20His%20social%20circle%20is%20full%20of%20other%20immigrants%20to%20the%20US%E2%80%94Africans%2C%20Hispanics%2C%20Arabs%2C%20and%20everyone%20else%20in%20between.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20what%20about%20Indians%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20that%20despite%20living%20in%20Houston%2C%20a%20city%20with%20the%20largest%20South%20Asian%20population%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Mo%20has%20managed%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20them%20in%20both%20seasons.%20Just%20like%20Mo%20has%20managed%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20October%207%2C%202023.%20According%20to%20the%202020%20census%2C%20Houston%20is%20home%20to%20about%20165%2C000%20Indians%2C%20the%20seventh-largest%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Culture%20And%20Divide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Hispanic%20and%20Vietnamese%20immigrants%2C%20Indians%20account%20for%20the%20single%20largest%20immigrant%20community%20in%20Houston.%20So%20why%20does%20Mo%20never%20interact%20with%20one%3F%20He%20grew%20up%20in%20Alief%2C%20a%20working-class%20suburb%20in%20southwest%20Houston%2C%20which%20was%20the%20most%20culturally%20and%20ethnically%20diverse%20school%20district%20in%20the%20US%20in%201996.%20A%20news%20report%20on%20Alief%20in%202006%20sums%20it%20up%20succinctly%20in%20one%20sentence%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20district's%2047%2C000%20students%20speak%20nearly%2070%20tongues.%E2%80%9D%20Yet%2C%20we%20do%20not%20see%20a%20single%20Indian%20in%20Mo's%20immigrant%20universe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20it%20be%20owing%20to%20the%20cultural%20insularity%20that%20Indian%20immigrants%20are%20(in)famous%20for%3F%20A%20Carnegie%20survey%20from%202021%20found%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20Americans%E2%80%94especially%20members%20of%20the%20first%20generation%E2%80%94tend%20to%20socialise%20with%20other%20Indian%20Americans.%20Internally%2C%20the%20social%20networks%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20are%20more%20homogenous%20in%20terms%20of%20religion%20than%20either%20Indian%20region%20(state)%20of%20origin%20or%20caste%E2%80%9D.%20Another%20relevant%20finding%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdivisions%20in%20India%20are%20being%20reproduced%20within%20the%20Indian%20American%20community%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%2C%20then%2C%20possible%20that%20Indian%20immigrants%2C%20primarily%20Hindus%2C%20choose%20to%20have%20minimal%20consociational%20engagement%20with%20Mo's%20community%3F%20Maybe%2C%20therefore%2C%20Indians%20are%20not%20even%20a%20footnote%20in%20Mo's%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMo%20is%20not%20entirely%20blameless%2C%20either.%20Devout%20Muslims%2C%20the%20Najjars%20are%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20embracing%20non-Muslims%20in%20the%20family's%20fold.%20Religion%20dictates%20their%20worldview%20as%20much%20as%20their%20regional%20identity%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstateless%E2%80%9D%20Palestinians.%20Yusra%2C%20Mo's%20mother%2C%20disapproves%20of%20his%20relationship%20with%20Mexican%20Maria%2C%20who%20wears%20her%20Catholicism%20on%20her%20sleeve%20as%20a%20tattoo.%20When%20Maria%20starts%20a%20rebound%20relationship%20with%20an%20Israeli-Jewish%20guy%20called%20Guy%2C%20she%20does%20so%20knowing%20that%20Mo%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20forgive%20that%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20her%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20'Elite'%20Immigrant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20maybe%20there's%20another%20explanation%20for%20the%20absence%20of%20Indian%20immigrants%20in%20this%20beloved%20story%20of%20the%20immigrant%20realities%20in%20the%20US.%20A%202023%20Pew%20survey%20shows%20that%20the%20median%20income%20of%20the%20immigrant%20Indian%20households%20is%20%E2%80%9Cgreater%20than%20the%20median%20household%20income%20among%20Asian%20Americans%20overall%E2%80%9D.%20So%2C%20Mo's%20tattoo%20artist%20friend%2C%20who%20is%20also%20doubling%20as%20an%20emergency%20surgeon%20suturing%20his%20bullet%20graze%2C%20and%20his%20codeine%20dealer%2C%20a%20fellow%20hustler%2C%20is%20a%20man%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%2FChinese%20origin.%20It%20is%20the%20underbelly%20of%20the%20immigrant%20American%20society%20that%20makes%20up%20Mo's%20universe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMo%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98elite'%20immigrant.%20He%20realises%20this%20when%20he%20spends%20time%20first%20in%20a%20cartel's%20and%20later%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccoyote's%E2%80%9D%20dungeon%20in%20Mexico%2C%20holding%20prospective%20illegals%20with%20an%20American%20dream.%20Even%20though%20Mo's%20family%20is%20struggling%20financially%2C%20they%20didn't%20have%20to%20undertake%20a%20life-threatening%20journey%20to%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20those%20currently%20being%20deported%20to%20India%20had%20to.%20After%20paying%20a%20hefty%20sum%E2%80%94almost%20as%20much%20as%20the%20Rolling%20Stone%20figure%20of%20%2410%2C000%20quoted%20by%20Nick%2C%20Mo's%20childhood%20friend.%20Yet%2C%20upon%20landing%20in%20the%20US%20territory%2C%20is%20the%20shared%20misery%20of%20the%20mule%20%E2%80%9Cdunki%E2%80%9D%20route%20forgotten%20in%20the%20race%20to%20realise%20the%20American%20dream%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20India%20received%20%24125%20billion%20in%20remittances%2C%20a%20much%20more%20significant%20sum%20than%20the%20%2471.92%20billion%20in%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20(FDI)%20in%202023-24.%20Undocumented%20immigrants%2C%20living%20and%20working%20under%20deportation%20fears%2C%20send%20a%20bigger%20chunk%20of%20their%20earnings%20back%20home.%20Maybe%20this%20is%20why%20Indians%20do%20not%20frequent%20gaming%20arcades%20and%20clubs%20that%20Mo%20and%20his%20friends%20often%20haunt.%20And%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20doing%20so%20prefer%20to%20socialise%20among%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20reasons%20are%2C%20Indians'%20absence%20from%20this%20saga%20of%20immigration%20is%20conspicuous%20and%20demands%20a%20think%20about%20the%20home%20and%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%C2%A0a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739961060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fsksdervo_mo_625x300_19_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmo-diversity-and-the-indian-immigrant-in-the-us-7745840%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20an%20alien%20were%20to%20gain%20insights%20into%20the%20immigrant%20situation%20currently%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Netflix%20show%20Mo%20would%20act%20as%20a%20good%20gateway.%20Except%2C%20it%20might%20lead%20the%20alien%20to%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20no%20Indian%20immigrants%2C%20legal%20or%20illegal%2C%20in%20US%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmo-diversity-and-the-indian-immigrant-in-the-us-7745840%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yogi%20Adityanath%20Hits%20Back%20At%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Over%20%26quot%3BMrityu-Kumbh%26quot%3B%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fyogi-adityanath%5C%22%20targe