cleshow%2F118384667.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20xAI%20company%20has%20introduced%20Grok%203%2C%20a%20powerful%20new%20chatbot%20aimed%20at%20competing%20with%20OpenAI%E2%80%99s%20ChatGPT.%20Announced%20at%20the%20World%20Governments%20Summit%2C%20Musk%20described%20Grok%203%20as%20'scary%20smart.'%20It%20is%20accessible%20to%20Premium%20Plus%20subscribers%20on%20X%2C%20with%20a%20promising%20voice%20interaction%20feature%20expected%20within%20a%20week%2C%20enhancing%20the%20user%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-says-please-report-any-issues-in-grok3-ai-chatbot-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-responds%2Farticleshow%2F118384667.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yogi%20Adityanath%20Rejects%20Faecal%20Bacteria%20Report%2C%20Says%20Sangam%20Water%20Fit%20For%20Drinking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20refuted%20a%20report%20that%20said%20faecal%20bacteria%20present%20in%20water%20at%20many%20places%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20criteria%20of%20water%20fit%20for%20bathing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20water%20at%20the%20Sangam%20-%20the%20point%20where%20River%20Ganga%20meets%20River%20Yamuna%2C%20along%20with%20the%20mythical%20Saraswati%20-%20is%20%26quot%3Bfit%20for%20drinking%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrores%20of%20people%20have%20taken%20holy%20dips%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%20on%20Monday%20said%20high%20levels%20of%20faecal%20and%20total%20coliform%20were%20found%20at%20various%20locations%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20allegations%20that%20untreated%20sewage%20has%20been%20discharged%20into%20Rivers%20Ganga%20and%20Yamuna%20in%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20NGT%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%20which%20said%20the%20results%20of%20water%20quality%20monitoring%20on%20January%2012%20and%2013%20found%20the%20water%20was%20not%20fit%20even%20for%20bathing%2C%20let%20alone%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20significant%20number%20of%20people%20bathing%20in%20the%20river%20at%20Prayagraj%20during%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20especially%20on%20auspicious%20bathing%20days%2C%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20faecal%20concentration%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%2C%20addressing%20the%20UP%20assembly%2C%20also%20condemned%20people%20who%20spread%20misinformation%20against%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20Dharma%2C%20Maa%20Ganga%2C%20and%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20discussion%20here%2C%20more%20than%2056.25%20crore%20devotees%20have%20already%20taken%20their%20holy%20dip%20in%20Prayagraj...%20When%20we%20make%20baseless%20allegations%20or%20spread%20fake%20videos%20against%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%20Maa%20Ganga%2C%20India%2C%20or%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20it%20is%20like%20playing%20with%20the%20faith%20of%20these%2056%20crore%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20stampede%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20that%20killed%2030%20people%20on%20January%2029%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20his%20condolences%20are%20with%20the%20family%20members%2C%20and%20the%20government%20will%20help%20them%20in%20every%20possible%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20But%20how%20appropriate%20is%20it%20to%20politicise%20this%3F%20They%20(Opposition)%20have%20been%20against%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20since%20day%201...%20In%20the%20last%20session%2C%20the%20discussions%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20were%20underway...%20We%20would%20have%20discussed%20the%20plans%20and%20taken%20your%20suggestions%2C%20but%20you%20did%20not%20let%20the%20house%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20national%20president%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20asked%20what%20was%20the%20need%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh...%20The%20social%20media%20handles%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20used%20language%20which%20any%20civilised%20society%20would%20not%20use...%20Lalu%20Yadav%20called%20the%20Kumbh%20'faaltu'.%20Another%20partner%20of%20the%20SP%20%5BSamajwadi%20Party%5D%20said%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20has%20become%20the%20'Mrityu%20Kumbh'...%20If%20organising%20events%20related%20to%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20a%20crime%2C%20then%20our%20government%20will%20keep%20committing%20that%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20alluding%20to%20remarks%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20that%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20has%20become%20%26quot%3BMrityu%20Kumbh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739958660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fm85rdrcg_maha-kumbh-_625x300_18_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyogi-adityanath-rejects-faecal-bacteria-report-says-sangam-water-fit-for-drinking-7745331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20refuted%20a%20report%20that%20said%20faecal%20bacteria%20present%20in%20water%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20criteria%20of%20water%20fit%20for%20bathing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyogi-adityanath-rejects-faecal-bacteria-report-says-sangam-water-fit-for-drinking-7745331%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kashmiri%20Student%20Brutally%20Ragged%2C%20Assaulted%20At%20Karnataka%20Medical%20College%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20second-year%20MBBS%20student%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20at%2