w%2F118384351.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fafghan-embassy-warns-of-mass-expulsion-of-afghan-refugees-from-pakistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F118384351.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fafghan-embassy-warns-of-mass-expulsion-of-afghan-refugees-from-pakistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F118384351.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shankaracharya%20Backs%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Amid%20%26quot%3BMrityu-Kumbh%26quot%3B%20Remark%20Criticism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20over%20her%20%26quot%3BMrityu%20Kumbh%26quot%3B%20comment%2C%20but%20got%20a%20supporter%20in%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%2C%20the%2046th%20Shankaracharya%20of%20the%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20stampede%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%2C%20and%20other%20issues%20such%20as%20traffic%20jams%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20long%2C%20high%20level%20of%20faecal%20coliform%20in%20water%2C%20etc%20had%20criticised%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20massive%20religious%20gathering%20for%20bad%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Mrityu%20Kumbh...%20I%20respect%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20I%20respect%20the%20holy%20Ganga%20Maa.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20planning...%20How%20many%20people%20have%20been%20recovered%3F%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20in%20the%20Bengal%20assembly%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20stampede%20that%20killed%2030%20people%20on%20January%2029%20when%20crowds%20surged%20ahead%20of%20an%20auspicious%20day%20for%20taking%20a%20holy%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJP%20leaders%20from%20the%20Centre%20as%20well%20as%20Bengal%20strongly%20condemned%20Ms%20Banerjee%20over%20her%20comments%20which%20they%20said%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments%2C%20Shankaracharya%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20Maharaj%20alleged%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20organisers%20did%20not%20follow%20proper%20crowd%20management%20processes%2C%20a%20view%20that%20concurred%20with%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20claim%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20There%20was%20a%20traffic%20jam%20of%20300%20kilometres.%20If%20this%20is%20not%20mismanagement%2C%20then%20what%20is%20it%3F%20People%20had%20to%20walk%2025-30%20km%20with%20their%20luggage...%20The%20water%20coming%20for%20bathing%20is%20mixed%20with%20sewage%20water%20and%20the%20scientists%20don't%20consider%20it%20fit%20for%20bathing%2C%20yet%20you%20are%20forcing%20crores%20of%20people%20to%20bathe%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Jagadguru%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Your%20job%20was%20to%20either%20stop%20the%20drains%20for%20a%20few%20days%20or%20divert%20them%20so%20that%20people%20could%20get%20pure%20water%20while%20bathing...%20You%20knew%2012%20years%20ago%20that%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20would%20come%20after%2012%20years%2C%20why%20did%20you%20not%20make%20any%20effort%20in%20this%20regard%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20was%20known%20beforehand%20that%20so%20many%20people%20would%20come%20and%20there%20is%20only%20limited%20space%2C%20then%20a%20plan%20should%20have%20been%20made%20for%20it...%20You%20did%20not%20make%20any%20plans...%20False%20propaganda%20was%20spread%2C%20the%20talk%20of%20144%20years%20itself%20is%20a%20lie...%20Crowd%20management%20and%20hospitality%20principles%20were%20not%20followed...%20Even%20when%20people%20died%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20hide%20it%2C%20which%20was%20a%20grave%20crime.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20if%20someone%20calls%20it%20names%2C%20then%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20oppose%20it...%26quot%3B%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Bemetara%2C%20Chhattisgarh%3A%20On%20West%20Bengal%20CM%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20'Mrityu%20Kumbh'%20remark%2C%20Jagadguru%20Shankaracharya%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20Maharaj%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20There%20was%20a%20traffic%20jam%20of%20300%20kilometres%2C%20if%20this%20is%20not%20mismanagement%20then%20what%20is%20it%3F%20People%20had%20to%20walk...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpxDXWI5og7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FpxDXWI5og7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1892111243646992556%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2019%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20national%20spokesperson%20Pradeep%20Bhandari%20termed%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20comment%20on%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20as%20%26quot%3Bhate%20Sanatan%20and%20Hindus%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Bhandari%20also%20aimed%20at%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bhaters%26quot%3B%20of%20Hindus%20and%20Sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20was%20looking%20for%20Akbar%20in%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20still%20not%20come%20to%20visit%20Maha%20Kumbh...%20They%20are%20scared%20of%20Sanatan's%20unity%2C%20and%20their%20Hindu%20hatred%20is%20evident%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhandari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Jitendranand%20Saraswati%2C%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bhartiya%20Sant%20Samiti%2C%20said%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20feeling%20%26quot%3Brestless%26quot%3B%20on%20seeing%20the%20way%20Hindus%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20o