orm-ticket-sale-hc-tells-railways%2Farticleshow%2F118383908.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Champion's%20Trophy%3A%20How%20This%20Mini-World%20Cup%20May%20Decide%20India's%20ODI%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20glitzy%2C%20glamorous%2C%20and%20trendy%20T20%20cricket%20might%20become%2C%20the%20curious%20thing%20is%20that%20in%20the%20collective%20cricketing%20consciousness%2C%20the%20longer%20the%20format%2C%20the%20more%20weight%20a%20tournament%20seems%20to%20carry.%20Ask%20yourself%20this%3A%20how%20much%20of%20the%20hurt%20and%20pain%20of%20India%20losing%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20did%20the%202024%20T20I%20World%20Cup%20title%20win%20realistically%20take%20away%3F%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98not%20much'.%20After%20all%2C%20that's%20how%20most%20cricket%20fans%20felt.%20The%20%E2%80%98what-ifs'%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98if-onlys'%20of%20India's%20performance%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20last%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20continue%20to%20haunt%20many%20of%20us.%20Just%20like%20the%20disastrous%20Test%20tour%20of%20Australia%20recently.%20These%20will%20continue%20to%20sting%20until%20a%20like-for-like%20tournament%20is%20won%20comprehensively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Chance%20For%20Redemption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20chance%20to%20reassure%20the%20fans%20that%20the%20number-one-ranked%20ODI%20team%20in%20the%20world%20is%20actually%20capable%20of%20beating%20the%20best%20teams%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20such%20an%20important%20tournament%20for%20the%20men%20in%20blue.%20Somewhere%2C%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20fans%2C%20their%20faith%20in%20the%20team%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%20was%20shaken%20after%20that%20catastrophic%20evening%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20November%2019%2C%202023%2C%20and%20perhaps%20hit%20rock%20bottom%20when%20India%20lost%20a%20bilateral%20ODI%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2027%20years.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20now%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20exorcise%20those%20demons%20once%20and%20for%20all%20and%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20future%20of%20Indian%20ODI%20cricket%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20next%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20An%20ICC%20Title%20Is%20Important%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20go%20into%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20having%20played%20a%20total%20of%20just%20nine%20ODIs%20since%20losing%20the%20final%20of%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20coming%20off%20a%20comprehensive%203-0%20series%20win%20against%20England%20at%20home%20(albeit%20the%20English%20are%20ranked%20as%20low%20as%20seventh%20in%20the%20ODI%20rankings).%20Confidence%20levels%20will%20be%20high.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20team%20will%20be%20based%20in%20Dubai%20and%20away%20from%20most%20of%20the%20tournament%20buzz%20and%20cacophony.%20The%20Dubai%20stadium%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20packed%20to%20the%20rafters%20with%20largely%20expatriate%20and%20some%20travelling%20Indian%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20fan%20support%20is%20the%20last%20thing%20the%20management%20will%20be%20thinking%20about.%20The%20first%20big%20thing%20they%20want%20to%20get%20right%20is%20team%20combination.%20Remember%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20does%20not%20follow%20a%20system%20of%20knee-jerk%20reactions.%20In%20a%20team%20full%20of%20big%20names%2C%20just%20because%20someone%20is%20underperforming%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20matches%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20will%20be%20dropped.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20playing%20XI%20selection%20is%20absolutely%20crucial%20in%20a%20tournament%20like%20this%20one%2C%20where%20one%20slip-up%20could%20cost%20the%20team%20a%20place%20in%20the%20semi-finals.%20Though%2C%20having%20said%20that%2C%20under%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20we%20are%20probably%20likely%20to%20see%20most%20players%20being%20given%20a%20shorter%20rope%20than%20in%20the%20past.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20makes%20the%20intra-team%20environment%20all%20the%20more%20competitive%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20everyone%20in%20the%20system%20is%20focused%20on%20acquiring%20the%20perfect%20remedy%20for%20some%20of%20the%20wounds%20that%20are%20still%20fresh%E2%80%94an%20ICC%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Surprising%20Mix%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20decision%20that%20surprised%20many%20was%20the%20call%20to%20include%20as%20many%20as%20five%20spinners%20in%20the%20final%20squad.%20Now%2C%20that%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20decision.%20Indian%20spinners%20can%20be%20lethal%20in%20strangling%20opposition%20batters%2C%20but%20as%20many%20as%20five%20spin%20options%20seem%20a%20bit%20much%20perhaps%2C%20especially%20given%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20ILT20%20tournament.%20Fast%20bowlers%20held%20sway%20in%20what%20are%20winter%20conditions%20in%20the%20UAE.%20Nine%20out%20of%20ten%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20bowlers%20of%20the%20ILT20%20this%20time%20were%20pacers.%20Also%2C%20host%20nation%20Pakistan%2C%20who%20have%20picked%20only%20one%20specialist%20spinner%2C%20will%20also%20play%20India%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20pitch%20could%20well%20be%20one%20that%20gives%20little%20or%20no%20help%20to%20the%20tweakers.%20The%20management%20clearly%20likes%20to%20have%20various%20batting%20options%2C%20and%20in%20Axar%20Patel%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20the%20team%20has%20two%20genuine%20all-rounders%20who%20are%20also%20very%20effective%20spin%20bowlers.%20These%20two%20look%20like%20the%20two%20first-choice%20spinners%2C%20as%20of%20now.%20But%20then%2C%20you%20also%20have%20someone%20like%20the%20new%20and%20improved%20Varun%20Chakravarthy%2C%20who%20was%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20(14%20wickets)%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%20vs%20England%20and%20forced%20his%20way%20into%20the%20Indian%20ODI%20and%20then%20Champions%20Trophy%20squads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20you%20not%20play%20possibly%20the%20most%20attacking%20wicket-taking%20spin%20option%2C%20who%20is%20regularly%20challenging%20batters%20with%20his%20menacing%20dip%20and%20bounce%3F%20If%20you%20do%2C%20that%20means%20India%20will%20have%20three%20spinners%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%2C%20with%20perhaps%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20who%20can%20also%20elongate%20the%20batting%2C%20on%20the%20bench.%20There's%20no%20way%20Hardik%20Pandya%20will%20not%20make%20the%20cut%20for%20the%20playing%20XI.%20If%20he%20is%20bowling%20at%20full%20tilt%2C%20does%20the%20management%20decide%20to%20play%20two%20out-and-out%20pacers%3F%20It%20sure%20looks%20like%20we%20could%20see%20three%20spinners%20in%20the%20India%20XI.%20Is%20this%20a%20sign%20of%20things%20to%20come%20in%20ODIs%20in%20the%20sub-continent%3F%20Either%20way%2C%20for%20Chakravarthy%2C%20this%20could%20well%20be%20a%20career-defining%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Setup%20For%20Future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20what%20Team%20India%20did%20in%20the%203-ODI%20series%20vs%20England%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20we%20will%2C%20in%20all%20probability%2C%20see%20four%20specialist%20batters%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20first-choice%20wicketkeeper%2C%20followed%20by%20potentially%20three%20all-rounders%E2%80%94in%20all%20probability%20Hardik%2C%20Axar%20and%20Jadeja%E2%80%94followed%20by%20two%20genuine%20pacers%2C%20which%20could%20well%20be%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20third%20spinner%2C%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20Chakravarthy.%20If%20this%20combination%20works%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20lock%20for%20future%20ODI%20assignments%20in%20similar%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20bowling%20could%20also%20end%20up%20being%20India's%20Achilles'%20heel.%20There%20is%20no%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%E2%80%94someone%20who%20can%20take%20the%20pitch%20and%20the%20conditions%20out%20of%20the%20equation.%20Shami%20is%20back%20after%20an%20injury%20and%20hasn't%20hit%20his%20straps%20yet.%20If%20Hardik%20the%20bowler%20is%20not%20at%20his%20best%2C%20it%20would%20be%20unfair%20to%20expect%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20to%20deliver%20a%20single-handed%20impact.%20And%20if%20the%20Dubai%20tracks%20don't%20offer%20too%20much%20assistance%20to%20the%20spinners%2C%20that%20would%20just%20make%20matters%20worse.%20The%20management%20perhaps%20is%20hoping%20that%20spinners%20like%20Axar%20and%20Chakravarthy%2C%20who%20are%20not%20heavily%20pitch-dependent%2C%20can%20deliver%20regardless%20of%20the%20conditions.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20Dubai%20Capitals%2C%20who%20won%20the%20last%20edition%20of%20the%20ILT20%2C%20began%20with%20four%20pacers%20and%20two%20spinners%2C%20but%20had%20to%20then%20bring%20in%20another%20spinner%2C%20as%20the%20tracks%20got%20slower.%20Have%20Team%20India%20then%20got%20it%20absolutely%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20need%20to%20get%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20first-choice%20wicketkeeper%20absolutely%20right.%20If%20the%20England%20series%20was%20any%20indication%2C%20it's%20KL%20Rahul%20who%20will%20bat%20at%20either%20five%20or%20six.%20But%20do%20you%20then%20keep%20someone%20like%20Rishabh%20Pant%E2%80%94an%20out-and-out%20attacking%20batter%E2%80%94on%20the%20bench%3F%20Gambhir%20has%20gone%20on%20record%20to%20say%20that%20KL%20is%20the%20team's%20first-choice%20keeper%20and%20there's%20no%20way%20they%20will%20play%20two%20keeper-batters.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20this%20time%20could%20well%20be%20a%20watershed%20opportunity%20for%20KL%20Rahul.%20The%2032-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20a%20career%20ODI%20average%20of%20almost%2048%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20golden%20chance%20to%20cement%20his%20place%20in%20the%20side%20as%20the%20preferred%20keeper%2C%20ahead%20of%20Pant.%20He%20has%20the%20coach's%20backing%2C%20and%20after%20an%20underwhelming%20performance%20in%20the%20ODIs%20vs%20England%20(52%20runs%20in%203%20innings)%2C%20this%20is%20one%20opportunity%20he%20just%20can't%20afford%20to%20let%20go%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Reckoning%20For%20The%20Two%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20the%20million-dollar%20question%E2%80%94can%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20prove%20that%20they%20can%20still%20be%20considered%20solid%20long-term%20ODI%20options%3F%20The%20two%20batting%20stalwarts%20did%20show%20some%20signs%20of%20brilliance%20in%20the%20ODIs%20vs%20England%20recently%2C%20but%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20outing%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20real%20litmus%20test%20for%20them.%20Neither%20can%20realistically%20survive%20a%20below-par%20outing.%20The%20next%20edition%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20is%20over%20two%20years%20away%20and%20the%20pressure%20to%20call%20it%20quits%2C%20at%20least%20from%20this%20format%2C%20will%20just%20be%20too%20high%2C%20unless%20they%20can%20play%20tournament-defining%20knocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20to%20say%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739956620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fljb9dai8_india-bcci_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchampions-trophy-this-mini-world-cup-could-decide-indias-odi-future-7745323%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20chance%20to%20reassure%20the%20fans%20that%20the%20number-one-ranked%20ODI%20team%20in%20the%20world%20is%20actually%20capable%20of%20beating%20the%20best%20teams%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20upcoming%