paceX%20CEO%20out%20of%20the%20White%20House%20and%20was%20working%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20limit%20his%20influence%20over%20Trump.%20He%20claimed%20Mr%20Musk's%20ideas%20were%20part%20of%20a%20global%20system%20called%20%26quot%3Btechno-feudalism%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20described%20as%20a%20movement%20that%20valued%20technology%20over%20people%20and%20saw%20everything%20in%20digital%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bannon%20lambasted%20Mr%20Musk%20when%20the%20SpaceX%20CEO%20criticised%20Trump's%20new%20%26quot%3BStargate%26quot%3B%20project.%20The%20project%2C%20announced%20last%20month%2C%20is%20backed%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20Oracle%2C%20SoftBank%2C%20and%20MGX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20these%20companies%20didn't%20actually%20have%20the%20%24500%20billion%20needed%20for%20the%20investment.%20He%20also%20called%20the%20project%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThey%20don't%20actually%20have%20the%20money%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1881923570458304780%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20and%20Mr%20Altman%20have%20a%20long-standing%20disagreement%20which%20began%20when%20they%20parted%20ways%20on%20OpenAI%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20organization%20they%20co-founded%20in%202015.%20In%202018%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20ended%20the%20partnership%20and%20started%20a%20direct%20rival%20company%20called%20xAI%2C%20accusing%20Mr%20Altman%20of%20aborting%20the%20nonprofit%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739953860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fj013fjh8_elon-musk-trump-_625x300_07_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fparasitic-illegal-immigrant-ex-donald-trump-aide-stev