ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406039%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20getting%20information%20from%20through%20Dr%20SN%20Tiwari%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Mehra%20registered%20the%20seed%20with%20PPV%20%26amp%3B%20FRA%20(Protection%20of%20Plant%20Varieties%20and%20Farmers%20Rights%20Act)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wheat%20variety%2C%20which%20was%20named%20Narendra%2009%2C%20and%20was%20initially%20grown%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20proved%20to%20thrive%20in%20diverse%20conditions.%20It%20was%20successfully%20cultivated%20in%20places%20like%20the%20Brahmakumari%20Agriculture%20Unit%20in%20Mount%20Abu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20regions%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F388188%2Fharyana-farmer-jagpal-singh-phogat-beekeeping-honey-earns-crores%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20nearby%20states.%20The%20positive%20outcomes%20from%20these%20trials%20reinforced%20the%20potential%20of%20this%20variety%20to%20grow%20well%20in%20different%20climates%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20thrives%20in%20all%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20mountainous%2C%20plains%2C%20and%20everywhere%20in%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mehra.%20The%20individual%20grain%20count%20per%20stalk%20reached%2050-80%2C%20far%20exceeding%20the%20normal%2020-25%20grains%20in%20traditional%20varieties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinita%20Singh%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20farmer%20from%20U