d%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20allow%20women%20to%20test%20and%20develop%20their%20entrepreneurial%20ideas%20while%20receiving%20mentorship%20and%20guidance.%20In%20addition%20to%20benefiting%20themselves%2C%20the%20fellows%20have%20been%20able%20to%20bring%20about%20change%20in%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20mission%20to%20empower%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20small%20villages%20and%20towns%20of%20India%20that%20Dr%20Lalitha%20Iyer%20found%20her%20true%20calling.%20A%20former%20banker%20and%20consultant%2C%20she%20had%20always%20believed%20in%20the%20power%20of%20women%20to%20drive%20change%20%E2%80%94%20if%20only%20they%20had%20the%20right%20support.%20With%20this%20vision%20in%20mind%2C%20she%20founded%20Plustrust%20in%202008%2C%20hoping%20to%20create%20a%20space%20where%20women%20from%20the%20most%20marginalised%20communities%20could%20step%20forward%20and%20chase%20their%20dreams%20without%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20tell%20us%20that%20the%20fellowship%20has%20helped%20them%20gain%20self-confidence.%20Many%20women%20had%20never%20spoken%20to%20a%20man%20outside%20their%20family%20before%20they%20became%20fellows.%20Now%20they%20address%20village%20meetings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Lalitha%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fellowship%20lasts%20for%20six%20months%2C%20giving%20women%20financial%20backing%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20hands-on%20training%20to%20transform%20their%20ideas%20into%20reality.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fellows%20create%20a%20prototype%20of%20their%20idea%20in%20six%20months%2C%20and%20if%20they%20feel%20confident%2C%20they%20continue.%20The%20programme%20builds%20three%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20pe